Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.logging.loggers

Class NullLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.kernel.logging.loggers.NullLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filtered<LogEntry>, Flushable, Receiver<Transmittable>, NamedObject, Logger, Listener, Transceiver
    public class NullLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements Logger
    A logger that does nothing.

    The following code can be used to efficiently shut off all logging: 

     LogFactory.factory(NullLogger::new)
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
